I've already paid everyone's severance pay.

492
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,079
According to the contract,

493
00:39:42,079 --> 00:39:45,039
we have to give three month's salary to every employee.

494
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:46,639
I gave them an extra month.

495
00:39:47,159 --> 00:39:48,960
The entire company is under renovation now.

496
00:39:49,519 --> 00:39:51,440
Apart from the Design Department,

497
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:53,119
I've rented out the other offices.

498
00:39:53,289 --> 00:39:54,559
We don't need such a big space.

499
00:39:55,079 --> 00:39:58,119
Also, I found a few small projects...

500
00:39:58,119 --> 00:40:00,079
that were up for bidding.

501
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,480
I'm working on the proposals for that.

502
00:40:01,809 --> 00:40:03,239
You sure are generous.

503
00:40:03,239 --> 00:40:04,960
You even paid them an extra month's salary.

504
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:07,599
Don't talk about work while eating.

505
00:40:07,599 --> 00:40:08,769
- All right. - It'll affect your digestion.

506
00:40:08,769 --> 00:40:09,769
We won't talk about it anymore.

507
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:11,920
Look. The company is in your hands now.

508
00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:13,599
From now on, I won't get involved with anything.

509
00:40:13,769 --> 00:40:15,039
Didn't you say you'd stop talking about work?

510
00:40:15,039 --> 00:40:16,880
Okay. Ms. Zhang, let me say one last thing.

511
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,239
Fine. Go on.

512
00:40:18,519 --> 00:40:20,119
I've sold one of my villas.

513
00:40:21,119 --> 00:40:22,639
After I get the money,

514
00:40:22,769 --> 00:40:25,440
use it as a backup fund for the company.

515
00:40:25,599 --> 00:40:26,599
All right?

516
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,199
Do your best, Hou Jue.

517
00:40:28,809 --> 00:40:29,809
Okay.

518
00:40:32,329 --> 00:40:34,000
Who is it? Coming.

519
00:40:34,519 --> 00:40:36,159
- Open the door. - Who is it?

520
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,400
I'm coming.

521
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:39,480
It's Mr. Zhang.

522
00:40:39,480 --> 00:40:40,480
- Good morning, Ms. Zhang. - Come.

523
00:40:40,599 --> 00:40:41,599
Come on in.

524
00:40:41,599 --> 00:40:42,920
- Have you eaten? - Yes.

525
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,679
- I ate in the car. - Here, change your shoes.

526
00:40:44,679 --> 00:40:45,920
Okay, thank you.

527
00:40:47,159 --> 00:40:48,159
I'm here to see Mr. Hou.

528
00:40:48,289 --> 00:40:49,599
- Are you looking for me? - No.

529
00:40:49,599 --> 00:40:51,360
I'm looking for Mr. Hou Junior.

530
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,239
You...

531
00:40:54,239 --> 00:40:57,289
From now on, call him Mr. Hou and call me Uncle Hou.

532
00:40:57,289 --> 00:40:58,519
That way, you can differentiate us.

533
00:40:58,519 --> 00:40:59,599
Call me Monkey.

534
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,639
Don't be so rude.

535
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:04,119
Dad, you eat.

536
00:41:04,119 --> 00:41:05,480
- I'll go talk to him. - Go.

537
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:07,719
- Let's go to the study. Come on. - Okay.

538
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,519
- Here, this room. - Okay.

539
00:41:12,639 --> 00:41:15,039
I've found all of Wu Tian Yi's creditors.

540
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:18,329
They've agreed to transfer the debt to you.

541
00:41:19,639 --> 00:41:21,519
You just need to find the debtors...

542
00:41:21,719 --> 00:41:23,480
and have them sign a third-party agreement.

543
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:25,559
Then you just need to get it notarized.

544
00:41:26,079 --> 00:41:27,199
All right.

545
00:41:27,199 --> 00:41:29,360
That's great. I was afraid they wouldn't agree.

546
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:31,119
Things are a lot easier as long as they agree.

547
00:41:31,239 --> 00:41:33,840
Here's the debt transfer agreement that I drafted.

548
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:34,840
Take a look at it first.

549
00:41:39,519 --> 00:41:40,519
Okay.

550
00:41:41,289 --> 00:41:42,679
- I just need to sign it, right? - Yes.

551
00:41:47,119 --> 00:41:48,880
Here, Mr. Hou. Have some water.

552
00:41:52,440 --> 00:41:53,559
Look.

553
00:41:53,559 --> 00:41:57,039
Actually, Hou Jue may like to fool around,

554
00:41:57,679 --> 00:41:59,920
but he's quite diligent when it comes to crucial moments.

555
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:03,000
- That seems to be true. - Yes.

556
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,440
So don't be too anxious.

557
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:09,920
Yes, he has grown up.

558
00:42:11,159 --> 00:42:12,679
I should really let go.

559
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,000
Yes,

560
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:16,239
you should let go when it's necessary.